These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
City: london, miami
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, spy
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, surfing
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, december
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
2. the person traveling to miami is in an even position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is the person traveling to london##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| City      | london  | miami   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | crime   |
| Sport         | surfing | cycling |
| Birthday     | february | december    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, 7up
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, documentary
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, soccer
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, tram
1. the person who's sport is soccer is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching action movies is the person driving the tram##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Beverage          | milk     | 7up |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | action  |
| Sport           | soccer         | cycling     |
| Transport     | motorbike   | tram    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different nationalities: malaysian, turkish
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, entrepreneur
City: prague, rome
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
2. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the malaysian is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Nationality    | turkish     | malaysian |
| Job         | entrepreneur | accountant    |
| City         | prague         | rome        |
| Transport   | bike         | helicopter    |

