.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite
There 2 different types of food: strawberry, zucchini
The people use 2 different means of transport: car, bus
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, climbing
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the car##1
2. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | almond-milk |
| Food          | zucchini   | strawberry  |
| Transport         | car | bus     |
| Sport   | rowing  | climbing         |

