The people prefer 2 different types of sport: badminton, basketball
1. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is in an even position##4
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |
| Transport           | airplane | snowmobile |
| Birthday   | october    | july      |
| Pet           | mouse      | turtle          |
| Sport         | basketball | badminton       |

