3. the person watching comedy movies is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | water    |
| Cigar         | bongani        | baccarat |
| Pet         | frog          | goat     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy        | drama     |

 